'''''The Fourth Reich''''' ( '''El Cuarto Reich''' ), ni filime yerekana ikinamico yo muri Afurika y'Epfo mu 1990 iyobowe na Manie van Rensburg ikaba yarayikoranye na Gert Basson, Mark Jaffee, David Selvan, Bill Shapter na Reg Wessels muri Zastron films.   Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo itsinda ry’abakinnyi ba [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo, Ryno Hattingh yakinnye nka Robey Leibbrandt . Abakinnyi bashyigikiwe barimo Marius Weyers, Grethe Fox na Percy Sieff. Inkunga nayo yari nyinshi bakina amakinamico yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo.  

Iyi filime ivuga ku buzima Robey Leibbrandt, umukinnyi w'iteramakofe wo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo witabiriye imikino Olempike yo mu 1936 yabereye i Berlin. Mugihe mu mikino yakundwaga nabanazi agerageza kumushakira umukozi muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo. Leibbrandt yakiriye ingengabitekerezo y'Abanazi, byaje kurangira abaye umukozi wa Abwehr kuri Reich ya gatatu . Nkumukozi wa Abwehr, mu 1939 Leibbrandt yayoboye igikorwa cyo guhirika guverinoma [[Afurika y’Epfo|y’Afurika]] yepfo ishyigikiye ubumwe, ndetse no kwica Jenerali Jan Smuts, icyo gihe akaba yari Minisitiri w’intebe w’ubumwe bwa Afurika yepfo .

The Fourth Reich niyo yakozwe muri firime ihenze cyane mumateka ya sinema yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo. 

The Fourth Reich yakinnye neza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime kandi yakiriwe neza kandi isubirwamo neza. 

